makes up this difference and may\nconfuse attempts to discern Pop III stars with broadband colors. In a companion\npaper, we explore the consequences of evolving spectra of Pop III for the\nreionization of the IGM in both H and He. (ABRIDGED)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jun 2002 23:34:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Oct 2002 16:47:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
